title: Garcia Plays Dylan Again FLAC
description:
Garcia Plays Dylan Again

Legion Of Mary / Jerry Garcia Band / Jerry Garcia and John Kahn
Initial release : 2005

This CD was distributed in association with the double CD set;
Garcia Plays Dylan, Jerry Garcia Band / Grateful Dead, 2005 

A 3 track bonus CD distributed with copies of Garcia Plays Dylan that were pre-ordered from www.jerrygarcia.com.
  
Tracks
It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry /Jerry Garcia and John Kahn/Neighbors of Woodcraft, Portland, June 4,82
Tears of Rage / Jerry Garcia Band / Greek Theater, Berkeley on August 5, 1990 
Going, Going, Gone / Legion Of Mary / Keystone, Berkeley on May 22, 1975

Musicians
The musicians on the tracks are probably as follows.

It Takes a Lot to Laugh, It Takes a Train to Cry;
Jerry Garcia - guitar, vocals 
John Kahn - bass 

Tears Of Rage;
Jerry Garcia - guitar, vocals 
Melvin Seals - keyboards 
John Kahn - bass 
David Kemper - drums 
Gloria Jones - vocals 
Jackie LaBranch - vocals 

Going Going Gone;
Jerry Garcia - guitar, vocals 
Merl Saunders - keyboards 
Martin Fierro - saxophone 
John Kahn - bass 
Ron Tutt - drums
